{"tid":114122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安徽工廠大爆炸　全城瞬間進入白晝持續10秒","createTime":"2017-02-09T14:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T14:28:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":191,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0da386ec36e6a9318769b3eaecaaeeba97fe1c2","tid":114122,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>安徽工廠大爆炸　全城瞬間進入白晝持續10秒</strong><br />\n2017年02月09日04:08<br />\n<br />\n中國再傳工廠爆炸，晚間10點45分左右，安徽省銅陵市銅官區銅官大道附近的恆興化工廠突然竄出巨大蕈狀雲，整座城市瞬間變成白晝，持續時間約10秒左右，目前消防、救援工作正在進行中。當地消防向央視記者表示，可能是廠內一燃料庫發生丙酮爆炸，具體起火原因還不明，火勢目前已被控制，有兩名值班人員受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n《銅陵新聞網》指，發生爆炸的是工廠裡存放的高沸點溶劑罐發生爆炸，經排查目前無人員死亡。<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》報導，爆炸的恆興化工廠成立於2001年7月25日，<strong>事故前已停止生產。</strong><br />\n<br />\n《新華網》報導，兩名傷者是被玻璃劃傷，已赴醫院就醫。銅陵市公安局局長鄒河表示，初步調查情況來看，爆炸起因是燃料油品燃燒，不涉及危險化學物品。<br />\n<br />\n《人民網》報導，爆炸已導致3傷。家住附近的萬先生稱：「以為地震了，窗戶外頭火光衝天，看得到一朵巨大的蘑菇雲。」另一民眾說：「我的天，我媽剛說天怎麼一下變亮了，我就聽見門就像被人敲一樣，轟隆轟隆的，把我嚇一跳，還以為有人搶劫，後來安靜了就以為沒事了，結果又聽見救護車消防車的聲音，那時就推測是不是爆炸，結果一看真是化工廠&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/420_8e0e9238dda3eddf9d6c84fa8bd091b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F420_8e0e9238dda3eddf9d6c84fa8bd091b6.jpg&h=3d3c4c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/420_5712a446d6525ff689b1ac3a3eca4964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F420_5712a446d6525ff689b1ac3a3eca4964.jpg&h=6a0921d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/420_f0630996afaf68947876776e546144a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F420_f0630996afaf68947876776e546144a7.jpg&h=a98ee801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/420_7d879e0a8530e9331b754fc613566389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F420_7d879e0a8530e9331b754fc613566389.jpg&h=fc74c6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝《騰訊》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/420_d338a68858686d555fcff34b9bb72aac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F420_d338a68858686d555fcff34b9bb72aac.jpg&h=0f0817a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅陵消防隊提醒，消息須經官方審核才可發佈，也呼籲民眾「夜已深，早點休息」。　<br />\n翻攝微博<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170209/1051983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170209%2F1051983%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2af41371\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170209/1051983/</a>"},{"pid":"cff24cb612ea9cb58beef3199b92036dac99b50d","tid":114122,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50566371cc62cea4dca8afe5fc57ac95033c51f","tid":114122,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  輕輕正皮"},{"pid":"aca62d0e4e88bbad4fdefafaa5eb7ae6a662c99b","tid":114122,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"試核彈姐"},{"pid":"f96fb05e955f1fdc6f538cabd57d4010c48fec55","tid":114122,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c